.RE
.PP
\fBNote\fP
.RS 4
If dir is nullptr, use MAPP_DIR environment variable or default directory ~/menuapp 

.PP
file_spec should be a pre-allocated char array of size MAXLEN to hold the resulting file specification 
.RE
